hkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fukterminatejd&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDwvFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=5a622b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/ukterminatejd</a><br />\n<br />\n希望見到大家🔥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d6uORjj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd6uORjj.jpg&h=ab8d7ce9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E7HEdxJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE7HEdxJ.jpg&h=50f4a972&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xuvnbjr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXuvnbjr.jpg&h=ddc87e54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n順便宣傳埋呢兩個集會 已發不反<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HX6p859.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHX6p859.jpg&h=f4e17713&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZsT2rc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZsT2rc.jpg&h=359b5b12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fc451d668d26b9f96d4bf251e8b31074ee8a50bf","tid":1778510,"uid":175927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe47bffc486c430494ac7ce7fda110cd69bcbcff","tid":1778510,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"想自己出嚟開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:28:52.000Z","msg":"都叫既"},{"pid":"968bf59218f749b16253dfa5f4f6604c9bba0f7d","tid":1778510,"uid":175927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88112b8f8c6d4bddc899b0e183d4db083b6339cb","tid":1778510,"uid":8007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"好簡單做下mc 答少少嘢je"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"希望啦 成日搞到亂"},{"pid":"7bfb2f919a015a330224bc1ee634a83b74968849","tid":1778510,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"